奮する監視隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_082"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叫び声が二部隊の睨み合いを破った。"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punch_xshield", "channel": "2", "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_riot", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "その直後、素手で殴り合う音と、鈍器で骨肉が砕ける音が響いた。"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_082"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何が起きて――", "name": "監視隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_082"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "助けて！　助けてくれ！　こいつら全員狂ってやがる――", "name": "興奮する監視隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_082"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "このクソッタレ感染者ども、全員*ウルサススラング*狂ってやがる！", "name": "興奮する監視隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_082"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#10$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そうとも……", "name": "ランキン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#10$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1963_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お前らに思い知らせてやる。感染者の怒りと、狂気を。", "name": "ランキン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1963_1#5$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}